Top Places to Travel: BOSTON & NANTUCKET . . . On a crossover episode of “best ways to experience New England,” The White Elephant on Nantucket island is partnering with Mandarin Oriental, Boston to offer guests the “Two If By Land, Three If By Sea” package: a three nights on the island and two nights in the city getaway.
Which means the only barrier between you and a glorious winter vacation is choosing where to go.
